Command:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username":"testuser","password":"password123"}'

Output:
{"message":"User successfully registered. Now you can login"}

---

Command (Error - Missing password):
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username":"testuser"}'

Output:
{"message":"Username and password are required"}

---

Command (Error - Duplicate username):
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username":"testuser","password":"password123"}'

Output:
{"message":"Username already exists"}
